1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
What if your sneeze could start a pandemic?

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,000
It's all about R0, the reproduction number.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
If each case infects more than one other person, outbreaks can spiral out of control.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,800
Imagine a single infection leading to dozens.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:18,400
Research shows that accurate tracking of R0 is crucial.

6
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:20,400
Misleading data can cause panic.

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,600
So, understanding R0 helps us prepare, not sensationalize.

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,800
Knowledge is power.

9
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:30,000
Stay informed, stay safe, and don't forget to follow for more science insights!
